  <brief_title>Does Continued Use of Clopidogrel Into Surgery Cause Increased Perioperative Bleeding?</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of Clopidogrel Use in Peri-Operative General Surgery Patients: A Prospective Study</official_title>
